#sitestatus-box
    - let sitestatus_background = page.top_background
    .author-content.author-content-item.sitestatus.single(style=sitestatus_background ? `background: url(${sitestatus_background}) top / cover no-repeat` : "")
        .card-content
            .author-content-item-tips SiteStatus
            span.author-content-item-title 网站状态
            .content-bottom
            .tips 活着就是值得，不是吗？
            .banner-button-group
              a.banner-button(onclick='pjax.loadUrl("/link/")')
                i.anzhiyufont.anzhiyu-icon-arrow-circle-right(style='font-size: 1.5rem')
                span.banner-button-text 友情链接
    #sitestatus_main
        .pageContainer
            #reports.reportContainer
            #tooltip.tooltip(style="opacity: 0")
                #tooltipArrow.tooltipArrow
                #tooltipDateTime.tooltipDateTime
                #tooltipStatus.tooltipStatus
                hr
                #tooltipDescription.tooltipDescription
            #templates(style="display: none")
                #statusSquareTemplate.statusSquare(class="$color" data-status="$color")
                #statusLineTemplate.statusLine
                #statusStreamContainerTemplate.statusStreamContainer
                #statusContainerTemplate.statusContainer
                    .statusHeader
                        h6.statusTitle(title="$title") $title
                        // 修改此处，在新窗口打开链接
                        a.statusLink(href="$url", target="_blank") 🔗
                        .statusHeadline(class="$color") $status
                    // 占位用于插入 30 天记录
                    #statusStreamPlaceholder
                    .statusFooter
                        .statusCounts 成功: $success, 失败: $failure
                        .statusUptime $upTime in the last 30 days
        footer.footer-right
            | Forked from 
            a(href="https://github.com/AndersonHJB/SiteStatus") AndersonHJB's Open-Source SiteStatus.

